  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "We're now digging through the mud Looking all the light out on the unpolluted valley of mud See baby, all these star lights Flipping on me, yeah they're flipping on me Baby yeah, all these star lights Got my wings past the desires Lost in light, I lost my light Am I here to fight or am I here to make right what wrong right? Am I the right way that I should be inside of my drug factory? And said all these lights above me All the things came before me All these lights above me Can I do justice? Oh, in this star light I dream higher than I ever could Yeah, in my own star light I keep shooting my only for the head Only for the guy in my star light I fight for the libraries of my own ways Yeah, star light Praying for you, praying for you It's all I have Praying for you to win the lottery of fear Because you couldn't imagine Any way your life has started in front of you We're just a working mass, working club Coming up and feel the class Feel it fast, feel the class Fill it up and make it last There's a life for you Beyond the things that you thought were you Yeah, in the star light You'll find a little dream Higher than soaring above you You'll find in you The things that come back From our ancestors From the moment falling I find in night The peace to carry on Even though you're gone Even though I'm in a different stratosphere I feel Yeah, these star lights lead me home to pray I know that I will find a way",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 5.900000095367432,
      "text": "We're now digging through the mud",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 12.359999656677246,
      "text": "Looking all the light out on the unpolluted valley of mud",
      "start": 5.900000095367432
    },
    {
      "end": 17.020000457763672,
      "text": "See baby, all these star lights",
      "start": 12.359999656677246
    },
    {
      "end": 20.219999313354492,
      "text": "Flipping on me, yeah they're flipping on me",
      "start": 17.020000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 24.84000015258789,
      "text": "Baby yeah, all these star lights",
      "start": 20.219999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 28.260000228881836,
      "text": "Got my wings past the desires",
      "start": 24.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 31.979999542236328,
      "text": "Lost in light, I lost my light",
      "start": 28.260000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 37.099998474121094,
      "text": "Am I here to fight or am I here to make right what wrong right?",
      "start": 32.439998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 41.959999084472656,
      "text": "Am I the right way that I should be inside of my drug factory?",
      "start": 37.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 45.7599983215332,
      "text": "And said all these lights above me",
      "start": 42.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 49.599998474121094,
      "text": "All the things came before me",
      "start": 45.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 52.58000183105469,
      "text": "All these lights above me",
      "start": 49.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 55.63999938964844,
      "text": "Can I do justice?",
      "start": 52.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 60.81999969482422,
      "text": "Oh, in this star light",
      "start": 56.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 63.459999084472656,
      "text": "I dream higher than I ever could",
      "start": 60.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 67.94000244140625,
      "text": "Yeah, in my own star light",
      "start": 63.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 72.55999755859375,
      "text": "I keep shooting my only for the head",
      "start": 67.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 75.73999786376953,
      "text": "Only for the guy in my star light",
      "start": 72.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 80.13999938964844,
      "text": "I fight for the libraries of my own ways",
      "start": 75.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 82.69999694824219,
      "text": "Yeah, star light",
      "start": 80.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 86.83999633789062,
      "text": "Praying for you, praying for you",
      "start": 84.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 88.37999725341797,
      "text": "It's all I have",
      "start": 86.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 91.76000213623047,
      "text": "Praying for you to win the lottery of fear",
      "start": 88.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 94.54000091552734,
      "text": "Because you couldn't imagine",
      "start": 92.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 97.87999725341797,
      "text": "Any way your life has started in front of you",
      "start": 94.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 100.86000061035156,
      "text": "We're just a working mass, working club",
      "start": 97.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 102.62000274658203,
      "text": "Coming up and feel the class",
      "start": 100.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 104.33999633789062,
      "text": "Feel it fast, feel the class",
      "start": 102.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 106.30000305175781,
      "text": "Fill it up and make it last",
      "start": 104.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 108.68000030517578,
      "text": "There's a life for you",
      "start": 106.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 112.37999725341797,
      "text": "Beyond the things that you thought were you",
      "start": 108.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 115.37999725341797,
      "text": "Yeah, in the star light",
      "start": 112.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 118.5199966430664,
      "text": "You'll find a little dream",
      "start": 116.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 122.30000305175781,
      "text": "Higher than soaring above you",
      "start": 118.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 124.94000244140625,
      "text": "You'll find in you",
      "start": 122.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 127.08000183105469,
      "text": "The things that come back",
      "start": 124.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 128.3000030517578,
      "text": "From our ancestors",
      "start": 127.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 130.3000030517578,
      "text": "From the moment falling",
      "start": 128.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 132.16000366210938,
      "text": "I find in night",
      "start": 130.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 134.10000610351562,
      "text": "The peace to carry on",
      "start": 132.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 135.33999633789062,
      "text": "Even though you're gone",
      "start": 134.10000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 138.22000122070312,
      "text": "Even though I'm in a different stratosphere",
      "start": 135.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 139.33999633789062,
      "text": "I feel",
      "start": 138.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 143.72000122070312,
      "text": "Yeah, these star lights lead me home to pray",
      "start": 139.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 147.13999938964844,
      "text": "I know that I will find a way",
      "start": 143.72000122070312
    }
